## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test each module's subcommands with valid and invalid inputs
- Verify error handling produces meaningful messages
- Test configuration read/write operations
- Verify log rotation functionality

### Manual Verification
- Run `devops-cli --help` to verify help system
- Test each command module with `--help` flag
- Verify configuration file creation at `~/.devops-cli/config`
- Check log file creation and rotation
- Test error scenarios to verify error messages
